{"title":"React基础入门","uid":"7a37c88da425aab45250f6c6b40d71f1","slug":"React学习笔记","date":"2021-04-28T14:09:53.000Z","updated":"2021-04-28T14:09:53.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/React学习笔记.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/log.jpg","content":"<p>React基础入门笔记四篇 配合视频 使用效果更佳<br>初识入门：<a href=\"https://juejin.cn/post/7015185218638184462\">https://juejin.cn/post/7015185218638184462</a><br>组件编程：<a href=\"https://juejin.cn/post/7015402441298411533\">https://juejin.cn/post/7015402441298411533</a><br>生命周期：<a href=\"https://juejin.cn/post/7015766065183621156\">https://juejin.cn/post/7015766065183621156</a><br>脚手架使用：<a href=\"https://juejin.cn/post/7016278634348412964\">https://juejin.cn/post/7016278634348412964</a></p>\n<p>react学习01: <a href=\"https://docs.qq.com/doc/DSG1jdUJtQ3FYR1V1\">https://docs.qq.com/doc/DSG1jdUJtQ3FYR1V1</a><br>react学习02: <a href=\"https://docs.qq.com/doc/DSGhGZk9PUm1KVldv\">https://docs.qq.com/doc/DSGhGZk9PUm1KVldv</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://brucecai55520.gitee.io/my-notes/#/\">FENotes (gitee.io)</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"React-Router-6-BruceBlog-gitee-io\"><a href=\"#React-Router-6-BruceBlog-gitee-io\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"React Router 6 | BruceBlog (gitee.io)\"></a><a href=\"https://brucecai55520.gitee.io/bruceblog/notes/react/react-router6.html\">React Router 6 | BruceBlog (gitee.io)</a></h2><h2 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结\"></a>总结</h2><p>React 是 Facebook 开发的前端框架，核心思想是<strong>组件化</strong>和<strong>声明式 UI</strong>。</p>\n<p><strong>核心概念：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>组件</strong>：UI 的基本单元，可复用、可组合</li>\n<li><strong>Props</strong>：父组件传递给子组件的数据</li>\n<li><strong>State</strong>：组件内部管理的数据</li>\n<li><strong>JSX</strong>：在 JavaScript 中写 HTML 的语法糖</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>生命周期：</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>挂载</strong>：<code>constructor</code> → <code>render</code> → <code>componentDidMount</code></li>\n<li><strong>更新</strong>：<code>shouldComponentUpdate</code> → <code>render</code> → <code>componentDidUpdate</code></li>\n<li><strong>卸载</strong>：<code>componentWillUnmount</code></li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Hooks（函数组件）：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>useState</code>：管理状态</li>\n<li><code>useEffect</code>：处理副作用</li>\n<li><code>useContext</code>：跨组件传值</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>学习资源：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>官方文档：react.dev</li>\n<li>路由：React Router</li>\n<li>状态管理：Redux &#x2F; Zustand &#x2F; Jotai</li>\n</ul>\n<p>React 生态庞大，建议先掌握基础概念，再逐步学习路由、状态管理等进阶内容。</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"React 基础入门学习笔记，配合视频教程与实战项目快速上手...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":824,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","count":3,"path":"api/categories/前端.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":11,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#React-Router-6-BruceBlog-gitee-io\"><span class=\"toc-text\">React Router 6 | BruceBlog (gitee.io)</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93\"><span class=\"toc-text\">总结</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Dxc","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"Free will is not free. <br /> @ <b>公众号：精准拔草</b> <span style=\"display:inline;white-space:nowrap\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" fill=\"#07C160\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:4px\"><path d=\"M8.691 2.188C3.891 2.188 0 5.476 0 9.53c0 2.212 1.17 4.203 3.002 5.55a.59.59 0 01.213.665l-.39 1.48c-.019.07-.048.141-.048.213 0 .163.13.295.29.295a.326.326 0 00.167-.054l1.903-1.114a.864.864 0 01.717-.098 10.16 10.16 0 002.837.403c.276 0 .543-.027.811-.05-.857-2.578.157-4.972 1.932-6.446 1.703-1.415 3.882-1.98 5.853-1.838-.576-3.583-4.196-6.348-8.596-6.348zM5.785 5.991c.642 0 1.162.529 1.162 1.18a1.17 1.17 0 01-1.162 1.178A1.17 1.17 0 014.623 7.17c0-.651.52-1.18 1.162-1.18zm5.813 0c.642 0 1.162.529 1.162 1.18a1.17 1.17 0 01-1.162 1.178 1.17 1.17 0 01-1.162-1.178